  "A function is one-to-one (injective) if different inputs always produce different outputs. This is necessary for the inverse to be a function. Graphically, one-to-one functions pass the horizontal line test.": "函数是一对一(目标),如果不同的输入总是产生不同的输出。这对反向函数是必要的。图形化的一对一函数通过水平线测试。",
  "What does 'arcsine' (arcsin or sin^(-1)) represent?": "“ arcsine”( arcsin 或 sin%( 1) ) 代表什么 ?",
